data.description: SUPER CLEAN WELL CARED FOR HOME READY FOR A NEW OWNER. RECENTLY UPDATED LIVING AREA AND KITCHEN, COMPLETE WITH NEW FLOORING, PAINT, TRIM WORK, CABINETS, COUNTERTOPS, AND MORE! THE NEW OWNERS WILL ENJOY 2 LIVING AREAS, OR AN EXTRA LARGE ROOM TO MEET WHATEVER NEEDS DESIRED. 3 BEDROOMS, AND 2 BATHROOMS WILL PERFECTLY SERVE ANY FAMILY! THIS PROPERTY IS CONVENIENTLY LOCATED JUST MINUTES FROM US 75, FOR COMMUTING OR JUST GOING INTO SHERMAN TO SHOP OR DINE. THE S.F. DOES NOT REFLECT THE CONVERTED GARAGE. LARGE BACKYARD HAS STORAGE BUILDING THAT CAN BE USED TO STORE YOUR LAWN MOWER OR TOOLS, AND A LARGE SHELVED CLOSET IN THE EXTRA ROOM PROVIDES ADDITIONAL STORAGE. PLENTY OF ROOM IN FRONT TO ADD COVERED PARKING.  ROOF REPLACED AUG 2023.
